com.here.android.mpa.search
Class ReverseGeocodeRequest

java.lang.Object
  com.here.android.mpa.search.Request<Address>
      com.here.android.mpa.search.ReverseGeocodeRequest

public class ReverseGeocodeRequest
extends Request<Address>

The ReverseGeocodeRequest represents an extended Request used to retrieve Address data by way of Geocoder search services.

Note: the response to a ReverseGeocodeRequest is a single Address object.
